Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.98,0:00:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.88,0:00:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! Are you all right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize anyone was there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Your hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Emma?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really has been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face looked a bit better back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 1\NThe Gift
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such bad timing! That's just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I Emma?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I used to be a governess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well this is the Young Master\NI cared for, William Jones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Young Master...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you stopped wetting the bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of... Of course I have. A long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking back, I realize that the Jones family...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:04:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...had but a modest presence among the gentry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your father well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,0:05:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to come and see me,\Nbut you never did...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, after all this time, you finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never cease to amaze me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you never seen a maid before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably Mr. Graham.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem tense, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:05:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is... that woman\Nalways makes me feel uneasy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.62,0:06:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She used to be even more\Nfrightening, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I forgot my homework,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she'd make me sit\Nfacing the wall for an hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This brings back memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is me, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mistress talks about you sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.02,0:06:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I recognized you the moment we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.09,0:06:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's a bit embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly,\Nthis was taken on my 13th birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised she displays it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mistress doesn't have\Nany children of her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think she must\Nconsider you as a son?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so? She was\Nalways so angry with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just how she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you learn to like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emma?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There seems to have been a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Graham is apparently waiting\Nat the station. I will go and fetch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid that I cannot\Nspare you any more time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even retired people have busy schedules.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, inform me by letter\Nwhen you will arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you must remember your manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please visit me again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must tell me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears he forgot these.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's as careless as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. He can collect them next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you go deliver them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for your mistress...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and there's one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from me. I'll await your reply\Nwhen next we meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The post?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you make some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master, your father is calling for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we stop this "Young Master" business?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the Young Master, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father talks for hours.\NCan you tell him no?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly not, Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know? It's an airplane.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're surprisingly light on your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to write this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to turn everyone down...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd put your skills of\Nreading and writing to use in this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you wish. As long as\Nyou can work tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.09,0:11:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Kelly woman. She's a slave driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She never thinks about what other\Nresponsibilities we might have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Responsibilities, Al?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always either playing cards or drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He surely is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then again, we're just the same as you, Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go down to the Ruth and Bear again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A toast, to the God of beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Potatoes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Miss Emma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good day to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jones, what can I do for you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've kept something for a\Nspecial customer such as yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of this doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's chinoiserie. They're currently all the rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.43,0:13:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how do you feel about this invention?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is called a "tea-making clock".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a combination alarm clock\Nand teapot, quite a rare item...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jones?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please deliver that to my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Emma!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jones...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.41,0:14:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I didn't notice it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, your gloves...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. In fact, I was just\Nthinking of visiting the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jones...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you do me the honor...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...of taking a walk with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please sir, buy some flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This park wouldn't be so crowded\Nif it weren't for The Season.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, Sydenham's Crystal Palace\Nwas built here for the World Trade Festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm talking too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right... I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That large elm tree back there was\Napparently going to be chopped down, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a squirrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that earlier, you also couldn't...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my eyesight is somewhat...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I buy you a new pair of\Nspectacles as a present?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, of course!\NPlease let me buy them for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But really, I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Birds are flying...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flowers are blooming...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Children are falling over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, it's no problem at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. They only had one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you don't want a carriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you just rented that umbrella...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to be honest,\NI rather like walking in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.63,0:16:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, so do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll say goodbye here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your gloves...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, I'll come back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The poor flowers have wilted...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send my regards to the mistress.\NAnd please do think about the spectacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That he should send wilted flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really is careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I cut their stems...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By taking in a little air and water,\Nthey seem to have regained their freshness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the flowers weren't for me anyhow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sends his regards to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've broken another cup?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes you leave dust on the banisters.\NYou must be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:18:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear, I wonder who that dog belongs to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They might feel strange\Nuntil you're used to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The birds...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know...\Nhow beautiful this view was!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You don't need them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine, just as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me... You were looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.82,0:20:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, isn't there anything else\Nyou want instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.19,0:20:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you want.\NCan't you think of anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.37,0:20:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lace...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would love to have even\Na single lace handkerchief...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.28,0:20:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A handkerchief? A handkerchief!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, I'll buy you 100, maybe 200!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:20:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lace... It's been a dream of mine for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lace?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, Mr. Jones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've bought even more useless objects?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you spend so much time\Nevery day in that store?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No reason...
